American actress Julia Fox has said her relationship with rapper Kanye West was the best thing that happened to her. “It was the best thing that could have happened to me,” the actress said of their short-lived romance while speaking to ‘Entertainment Tonight’ at “The Batman” premiere in New York City on Tuesday. “It kind of brought a spark back into my life that I had kind of forgotten about”, she added. Fox and West met in Miami on New Year’s Eve.   I’m considering dropping out of Oxford University – DJ Cuppy     Segun Arinze to youths: get active in politics     Mohbad reunites with Naira Marley, others   The two quickly bonded and even traveled to New York City together within days of knowing each other. The 44-year-old Yeezy boss proceeded to spoil the “Uncut Gems” star with a hotel suite’s worth of clothes from Diesel. However, things quickly took a turn in February after the father-of-four shared a series of since-deleted Instagram posts, in an attempt to try and win back his then-estranged wife, Kim Kardashian. Fox and West ultimately called it quits after about six weeks of dating.